title: Grateful Dead Live at Carrier Dome, Syracuse U on 1983-10-22
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Wang Dang Doodle, Candyman, Minglewood Blues, Bird Song, Hell In A Bucket-> Day Job

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter, Terrapin Station-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away-> One More Saturday Night, E: Revolution

The Band without Robertson, with the Cate Brothers Opened
